    "Indeed, Hitchin [Hit92] showed that, for n > 2, the representations with [ρ] ∈ Hom(π 1 (B), PSL n (R))/PSL n (R) which can be continuously deformed to one taking values in the maximal compact subgroup PSO(n) all belong to a single connected component of the character variety (whose elements have the same topological type as those in the Hitchin component).",
    "But there are 2 (resp.",
    "5) other connected components when n is odd (resp. even).Remark 6.5.",
